<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.1.8">
<l>viraika maḻntameṉ karuṅkuḻal kāraṇam villiṟut taṭalmaḻaikku</l>
<l>niraika laṅkiṭa varaikuṭai yeṭuttavaṉ nilaviya viṭamtaṭamār</l>
<l>varaiva ḷantikaḻ matakari maruppoṭu malaivaḷa rakilunti</l>
<l>tiraiko ṇarntaṇai ceḻunati vayalpuku tiruvayin tirapuramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The luminous place of him who took up a mountain umbrella</l>
<l rend="indent">as the herd trembled due to the violent rain,</l>
<l>Having snapped the bow because of the soft, dark curls</l>
<l rend="indent">which wafted fragrances,</l>
<l>Is Tiruvayintirapuram where the dammed [up] swollen river flows into fields,</l>
<l rend="indent">tossing and carrying in [its] waves</l>
<l>Aquila [trees] that grew on the mountain, along with tusks</l>
<l rend="indent">of rutting elephants whose beauty glistens on hills covered with pools.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
